# Note: assets/bin contains the NPU Bridge which is required for the extension, 
# but usually we don't want to commit the whole self-contained bundle if it's large.
# However, for Raycast extensions, assets are often bundled.
# Given the project context, assets/bin contains many DLLs.
# I will exclude assets/bin for now but the user might want to include it later.

